function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/100986/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Amprenavir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, More', 'Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Dezocine, Opium, Pentazocine, Dihydrocodeine, Naloxone, Nalbuphine, Diamorphine, Acamprosate, Lofexidine, More', 1767369485);
